#. HTML: <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.11" id="11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: nīvaraṇappahāṇavaggo (bj) | nīvaraṇavagga (pts1)
msgctxt "an1.11-20:0.2"
msgid "2. Nīvaraṇappahānavagga "
msgstr "2. Giving Up the Hindrances "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:0.3"
msgid "11 "
msgstr "11 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.3, sc11.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā kāmacchando uppajjati uppanno vā kāmacchando bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, subhanimittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to sensual desire, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow like the feature of beauty. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.2"
msgid "Subhanimittaṃ, bhikkhave, ayoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva kāmacchando uppajjati uppanno ca kāmacchando bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you attend improperly to the feature of beauty, sensual desire arises, and once arisen it increases and grows.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.12" id="12"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:11.1.4"
msgid "12 "
msgstr "12 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc12.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā byāpādo uppajjati uppanno vā byāpādo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭighanimittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to ill will, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow like the feature of harshness. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.2"
msgid "Paṭighanimittaṃ, bhikkhave, ayoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva byāpādo uppajjati uppanno ca byāpādo bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you attend improperly to the feature of harshness, ill will arises, and once arisen it increases and grows.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.13" id="13"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:12.1.4"
msgid "13 "
msgstr "13 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc13.1
#. VAR: thinamiddhaṃ → thīnamiddhaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: tandī → tandi (s1-3, mr)
#. VAR: vijambhitā → vijambhikā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā thinamiddhaṃ uppajjati uppannaṃ vā thinamiddhaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, arati tandī vijambhitā bhattasammado cetaso ca līnattaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to dullness and drowsiness, or, when they have arisen, makes them increase and grow like discontent, sloth, yawning, sleepiness after eating, and mental sluggishness. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.2"
msgid "Līnacittassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva thinamiddhaṃ uppajjati uppannañca thinamiddhaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you have a sluggish mind, dullness and drowsiness arise, and once arisen they increase and grow.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.3"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.14" id="14"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:13.1.4"
msgid "14 "
msgstr "14 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc14.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā uddhaccakukkuccaṃ uppajjati uppannaṃ vā uddhaccakukkuccaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cetaso avūpasamo. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to restlessness and remorse, or, when they have arisen, makes them increase and grow like an unsettled mind. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.2"
msgid "Avūpasantacittassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva uddhaccakukkuccaṃ uppajjati uppannañca uddhaccakukkuccaṃ bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you have no peace of mind, restlessness and remorse arise, and once arisen they increase and grow.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.15" id="15"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:14.1.4"
msgid "15 "
msgstr "15 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.4, sc15.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannā vā vicikicchā uppajjati uppannā vā vicikicchā bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, ayonisomanasikāro. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to doubt, or, when it has arisen, makes it increase and grow like improper attention. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.2"
msgid "Ayoniso, bhikkhave, manasi karoto anuppannā ceva vicikicchā uppajjati uppannā ca vicikicchā bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya saṃvattatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you attend improperly, doubt arises, and once arisen it increases and grows.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.16" id="16"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:15.1.4"
msgid "16 "
msgstr "16 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc16.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā kāmacchando nuppajjati uppanno vā kāmacchando pahīyati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, asubhanimittaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents sensual desire from arising, or, when it has arisen, abandons it like the feature of ugliness. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.2"
msgid "Asubhanimittaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva kāmacchando nuppajjati uppanno ca kāmacchando pahīyatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you attend properly to the feature of ugliness, sensual desire does not arise, or, if it has already arisen, it’s given up.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.17" id="17"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:16.1.4"
msgid "17 "
msgstr "17 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc17.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppanno vā byāpādo nuppajjati uppanno vā byāpādo pahīyati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, mettā cetovimutti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents ill will from arising, or, when it has arisen, abandons it like the heart’s release by love. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.2"
msgid "Mettaṃ, bhikkhave, cetovimuttiṃ yoniso manasi karoto anuppanno ceva byāpādo nuppajjati uppanno ca byāpādo pahīyatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you attend properly on the heart’s release by love, ill will does not arise, or, if it has already arisen, it’s given up.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.18" id="18"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:17.1.4"
msgid "18 "
msgstr "18 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc18.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā thinamiddhaṃ nuppajjati uppannaṃ vā thinamiddhaṃ pahīyati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, ārambhadhātu nikkamadhātu parakkamadhātu. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents dullness and drowsiness from arising, or, when they have arisen, gives them up like the elements of initiative, persistence, and vigor. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.2"
msgid "Āraddhavīriyassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva thinamiddhaṃ nuppajjati uppannañca thinamiddhaṃ pahīyatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you’re energetic, dullness and drowsiness do not arise, or, if they’ve already arisen, they’re given up.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.19" id="19"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:18.1.4"
msgid "19 "
msgstr "19 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc19.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannaṃ vā uddhaccakukkuccaṃ nuppajjati uppannaṃ vā uddhaccakukkuccaṃ pahīyati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, cetaso vūpasamo. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents restlessness and remorse from arising, or, when they have arisen, gives them up like peace of mind. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.2"
msgid "Vūpasantacittassa, bhikkhave, anuppannañceva uddhaccakukkuccaṃ nuppajjati uppannañca uddhaccakukkuccaṃ pahīyatī”ti. "
msgstr "When your mind is peaceful, restlessness and remorse do not arise, or, if they’ve already arisen, they’re given up.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.20" id="20"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.11-20:19.1.4"
msgid "20 "
msgstr "20 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.5, sc20.1
msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.1"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi yena anuppannā vā vicikicchā nuppajjati uppannā vā vicikicchā pahīyati yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, yonisomanasikāro. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that prevents doubt from arising, or, when it has arisen, gives it up like proper attention. "

msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.2"
msgid "Yoniso, bhikkhave, manasi karoto anuppannā ceva vicikicchā nuppajjati uppannā ca vicikicchā pahīyatī”ti. "
msgstr "When you attend properly, doubt does not arise, or, if it’s already arisen, it’s given up.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.11-20:20.1.4"
msgid "Nīvaraṇappahānavaggo dutiyo. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></section></body></html>
